title: Grateful Dead Live at Madison Square Garden on 1991-09-13
description:
Set 1

Touch Of Gray, Wang Dang Doodle, Peggy-O, Big River, Cumberland Blues, Althea, When I Paint My Masterpiece, Bird Song

Set 2

Victim Or The Crime, Scarlet Begonias-> Fire On The Mountain, Drums-> Jam-> The Other One-> Stella Blue-> Throwing Stones, Not Fade Away, E: Knockin' On Heaven's Door

reviews.review_text: Best Aud source? Both the gems version and the bk4011 pull are both good sounding.  I like this one a little more.  You can really feel the room, to go along with the punchy sound.
